Take Rava and curd (Dahi) mix  them and let them sattle for 30 min 
AFTER 30 MIN 
 cut and add spanich and onnoin and let it sattle for 10 min again
 TILL THE TIME
 Take the idli maker and put oil with the help of a brush
 and put it on gas at a low level
AFTER 10 MIN 
Add the ingerdents wich we made with curd etc. ,put it in
 the idli maker after some time turn over the
 appe and cover it with something (plate )add sprinkles of
rai on it ,  when it gets in a eatable manner  or say it get
in a manner that we can hold take it out and for a beautiful
 finish put some sous and serve ;
 ENJOY.
